  <section id="story">
    <h2>Our Story</h2>
    <p>Coffee Haven began in 2015 as a small neighborhood café with a big dream — to make every cup a moment of peace and connection. Over the years, we've grown from a humble shop into a community hub for coffee lovers, freelancers, and friends alike.</p>
    <p>Our founder, <strong>Regina Santos</strong>, envisioned a place where passion for coffee meets sustainable living. Today, we proudly source our beans from fair-trade farms and reduce waste with eco-friendly packaging.</p>
  </section>

  <section id="team">
    <h2>Meet Our Team</h2>
    <div>
      <h3>Regina Santos - Founder</h3>
