      <h3>Mia Dela Cruz - Marketing Lead</h3>
      <p>Spreads the word about our events and community collaborations.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="mission">
    <h2>Our Mission</h2>
    <p>We aim to brew not just great coffee, but meaningful experiences. Our mission is to promote sustainability, creativity, and connection—one cup at a time.</p>
  </section>

